Lindsay - Season 1, Episode 1




Part 1

Upon completion of her sixth stay in court-ordered rehab, Lindsay Lohan has decided to leave Los Angeles for a fresh start. After going through a decade's worth of belongings, Lindsay arrives in New York. Accompanied with her new assistant, Matt, and her sober coach, Michael, she moves into a hotel and begins her search for an apartment.




Original Air Date: 09-Mar-2014
